title: Counter Strike 1.6 Windows 8.1 Patch (Fixed)
description:
This is the right version to download!

===================================================================================

This patch will make your Counter-Strike 1.6 run on Windows 8.1 (or any other 

previous version of Windows).


The patch includes protector which secures your game client from any potential 

damage from internet servers and protects it from ads.

===================================================================================

Enjoy!
